OL,3,CCourt hears how boy warned father of
OL,4,C'drunk drivers' minutes before their
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FJersey's Royal Court has seen the
OL,8,Fvideo made by an 11-year-old boy where
OL,9,Fhe says "Imagine being hit by a drunk
OL,10,Fdriver" minutes before he died in a
OL,11,Froad traffic collision.
OL,13,FCharlie Lowe, 11, and his father Dean,
OL,14,F48, were killed on La Rue de Fauvic,
OL,15,Fin Grouville in August 2023.
