OL,3,CCourt hears how boy warned father of
OL,4,C'drunk drivers' minutes before their
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe footage was shown on the first day
OL,8,Fof the trial of 29-year-old Dylan John
OL,9,FPounds, who denies causing death by
OL,10,Fdangerous driving, and death by
OL,11,Fcareless driving whilst under the
OL,12,Finfluence of drink or drugs.
OL,14,FThe prosecution alleges that Pounds
OL,15,Fhad started drinking around midday on
OL,16,FSaturday 5 August and consumed around
OL,17,F9 alcoholic drinks over a rough period
OL,18,Fof nine hours.
