OL,3,CCourt hears how boy warned father of
OL,4,C'drunk drivers' minutes before their
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThey allege that Pounds first visited
OL,8,Fthe Union Inn before going to The
OL,9,FPembroke and leaving his work van
OL,10,Fthere.
OL,12,FFootage appears to show Pounds in The
OL,13,FPembroke at the same time as Dean
OL,14,FLowe, who was there with his son.
OL,16,FThe prosecution says that Pounds had
OL,17,Fsix alcoholic drinks at The Pembroke,
OL,18,Fwith footage showing Pounds leaving
OL,19,Fhis van at the pub and being driven by
OL,20,Fothers to the Dolphin Hotel.
