OL,3,CCourt hears how boy warned father of
OL,4,C'drunk drivers' minutes before their
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe prosecution alleges the footage
OL,8,Fshowing Pounds getting a lift shows he
OL,9,Fknew he was already too inebriated to
OL,10,Fdrive.
OL,12,FAfter more drinks at the Dolphin, the
OL,13,Fprosecution says Pounds left and made
OL,14,Fhis way back to The Pembroke via bus.
OL,16,FThe prosecution alleges the bus' CCTV
OL,17,Ffootage shows one of Pounds' friends
OL,18,Fshaking his head as Pounds decided to
OL,19,Fget off the bus, alleging they were
OL,20,Fasking Pounds not to retrieve his van
OL,21,Fand drive home.
