OL,3,CCourt hears how boy warned father of
OL,4,C'drunk drivers' minutes before their
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe prosecution then showed a video to
OL,8,Fthe court that Charlie Lowe took
OL,9,Fminutes before his death.
OL,11,FIt shows Charlie and his father
OL,12,Fwalking home towards St Clement's
OL,13,FChurch in Grouville.
OL,15,FIn the footage, Charlie can be heard
OL,16,Fsaying "Let's hope we don't get hit by
OL,17,Fa drunk driver".
OL,19,FMinutes later, Charlie and Dean were
OL,20,Fstruck by Pounds' van.
