OL,3,CCourt hears how boy warned father of
OL,4,C'drunk drivers' minutes before their
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe prosecution showed independent
OL,8,Fexpert analysis showing Pounds was
OL,9,Fdriving between 41 and 50mph. They add
OL,10,Fthat Pounds was likely travelling at
OL,11,F47mph when he hit Charlie and Dean
OL,12,FLowe.
OL,14,FThe prosecution alleges there were no
OL,15,Fsigns that Pounds attempted to brake.
OL,17,FIn May 2024, Pounds pled guilty to
OL,18,Fcausing the deaths of Charlie and Dean
OL,19,FLowe by careless driving and failing
OL,20,Fto stop and report an accident.
