OL,7,FHowever, he has denied causing death
OL,8,Fby dangerous driving, and death by
OL,9,Fcareless driving whilst under the
OL,10,Finfluence of drink or drugs, as well
OL,11,Fas a separate count of dangerous
OL,12,Fdriving.
OL,14,FThe trial continues and is due to take
OL,15,Feight days.
